# Project Structure Rules
tags: ["structure", "paths", "backups"]
appliesTo: ["GPT", "CursorAgent", "Ghost"]
enforce: true
priority: high

## Rules

- All patch paths must use hardened absolute paths (no `~/` or relative).
- Backups must follow the format: `YYMMDD-UTC_vX.X.X-description_backup_[project].tar.gz`.
- Task filenames must follow Cursor-compliant semantic format.
- No `.tar.gz` backups may occur unless system is stable.